OL,3,CMum who lost brother to suicide hopes
OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,FA former teacher whose brother took
OL,7,Fhis own life just days before she was
OL,8,Fdue to start a Masters in mental
OL,9,Fhealth studies says she hopes her
OL,10,Fresearch will prevent other suicides.
OL,12,FNina Smith, from Wigan, was two weeks
OL,13,Faway from beginning her course at Edge
OL,14,FHill University in Ormskirk,
OL,15,FLancashire, when her brother Will died.
OL,17,FShe has now devoted her studies to
OL,18,Flooking into how schools can teach
OL,19,Fsuicide prevention - something the are
OL,20,Fcalling to be put on the National
OL,21,FCurriculum.
