OL,3,CMum who lost brother to suicide hopes
OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,FWill was 30 when he took his own life
OL,7,Fin August 2021. His daughter Paige was
OL,8,Fjust five at the time.
OL,10,FNina says his death had a devastating
OL,11,Feffect on all their lives.
OL,13,F"I was so excited, going back to
OL,14,Funiversity, I was going to do this
OL,15,Fsuicide prevention research - it was
OL,16,Flike a dream come true," she said.
OL,18,F"And then I got this knock on the
OL,19,Fdoor, telling me he had taken his own
OL,20,Flife.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
