OL,3,CMum who lost brother to suicide hopes
OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,F"And every time I hear about another
OL,7,Fsuicide I'm transported back to that
OL,8,Fknock at the door.
OL,10,F"When I went to mum's house and she
OL,11,Fwas on the floor, she was screaming
OL,12,Fand the conversation I had to have
OL,13,Fwith my five-year-old niece and I had
OL,14,Fto be the one to tell her her daddy
OL,15,Fhad died."
