OL,6,FNina vowed to continue her studies and
OL,7,Fwas accepted for a Churchill
OL,8,FFellowship where she is currently
OL,9,Flooking into how schools can
OL,10,Feffectively incorporate suicide
OL,11,Fprevention into the curriculum, with
OL,12,Fthe goal of informing policy and
OL,13,Fpractice in the UK.
OL,15,FNina said: "As a former teacher I have
OL,16,Fseen that the number of children
OL,17,Fstruggling with their mental health is
OL,18,Fincreasing and the severity of that
OL,19,Fmental ill health is also increasing.
