OL,3,CMum who lost brother to suicide hopes
OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,F"When my brother died I didn't know
OL,7,Fthe signs to look out for and if I had
OL,8,FI might have been able to help.
OL,10,F"I want to do something to help now."
OL,12,FNina's Fellowship proposal was
OL,13,Finspired by school-based research
OL,14,Fcarried out during her time at Edge
OL,15,FHill while studying MSc Sport,
OL,16,FPhysical Activity and Mental Health,
OL,17,Fsupported by a bursary provided by
OL,18,FEverton in the Community, the official
OL,19,Fcharity of Everton Football Club.
