OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,FNina's research also reveals that
OL,7,Fteachers are currently struggling to
OL,8,Fcope with an escalating problem of
OL,9,Fpoor mental health in schools.
OL,11,FNina said: "Teachers said they were
OL,12,Fincreasingly having to try to support
OL,13,Fpupils who were self-harming, even
OL,14,Fattempting suicide on school property,
OL,15,Fwithout adequate training or support
OL,16,Ffrom outside agencies.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
