OL,3,CMum who lost brother to suicide hopes
OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,F"No matter how hard they were trying,
OL,7,Fthey felt like they just couldn't give
OL,8,Fthe support to their pupils that they
OL,9,Fneeded, and they were going home
OL,10,Fworrying about their pupil's mental
OL,11,Fhealth, and wondering would they get
OL,12,Fan awful phone call in the morning.
OL,14,F"So they were just left to do their
OL,15,Fbest, which without qualifications,
OL,16,Ffunding and resources, could only ever
OL,17,Fprovide so much help for those pupils."
