OL,6,FHer research is looking at best
OL,7,Fpractice across the world, and she has
OL,8,Fjust returned from Melbourne,
OL,9,FAustralia where she's been assessing
OL,10,Fhow the programmes already being used
OL,11,Fthere, are working.
OL,13,FOne of the programmes she has been
OL,14,Fobserving is Multi-Modal Approach to
OL,15,FPreventing Suicide in Schools,
OL,16,Fotherwise known as MAPSS - which is
OL,17,Fthe same programme that is currently
OL,18,Fbeing as part of a groundbreaking
OL,19,Fstudy by John Moores University.
