OL,4,Cto help others
OL,6,FNina's passion for change has also
OL,7,Fattracted the support of key suicide
OL,8,Fprevention campaigners 3 Dads Walking
OL,9,Fwho are lobbying to make suicide
OL,10,Fprevention a compulsory part of the UK
OL,11,Fschool curriculum.
OL,13,FMeanwhile at Edge Hill University -
OL,14,Fthe biggest provider of teacher
OL,15,Ftraining in the North West - they are
OL,16,Fexploring how to embed Nina's findings
OL,17,Finto their current training of teacher
OL,18,Fstudents.
